---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import heroImage from "../images/home.jpg";
---

<section class="relative py-24 overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background Image with overlay -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full">
    <Image
      src={heroImage}
      alt="Interior Design Background"
      class="w-full h-full object-cover object-center"
      quality={90}
      style="filter: brightness(0.85)"
    />
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-400/60 via-orange-500/40 to-amber-900/70 mix-blend-multiply"
    >
    </div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-white/10 to-transparent">
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <h2
        class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-orange-900 drop-shadow-lg mb-4 tracking-tight"
      >
        Our Promise to You
      </h2>
      <p
        class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-amber-900/90 font-medium max-w-2xl mx-auto"
      >
        Experience the perfect blend of creativity, quality, and care in every
        project we deliver.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Custom Accordion -->
    <div
      class="rounded-3xl shadow-2xl bg-white/80 border-4 border-amber-200/60 backdrop-blur-md p-8 space-y-6"
    >
      <details
        class="group rounded-xl border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50/80 transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden"
      >
        <summary
          class="flex items-center cursor-pointer px-6 py-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-orange-700 group-open:bg-amber-100/80 group-open:text-orange-900 transition-all duration-300"
        >
          <span
            class="mr-4 flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-400 to-orange-500 flex items-center justify-center shadow-md"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 text-white"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              ><path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M12 4v16m8-8H4"></path></svg
            >
          </span>
          Award-Winning Design Team
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6 pt-2 text-lg text-orange-800">
          Our team of passionate designers brings global expertise and a keen
          eye for detail, ensuring every space is both beautiful and functional.
        </div>
      </details>
      <details
        class="group rounded-xl border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50/80 transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden"
      >
        <summary
          class="flex items-center cursor-pointer px-6 py-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-orange-700 group-open:bg-amber-100/80 group-open:text-orange-900 transition-all duration-300"
        >
          <span
            class="mr-4 flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-400 to-amber-500 flex items-center justify-center shadow-md"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 text-white"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              ><path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg
            >
          </span>
          Bespoke Solutions for Every Client
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6 pt-2 text-lg text-orange-800">
          We listen, collaborate, and tailor every design to your unique
          lifestyle, taste, and aspirations—no two projects are ever the same.
        </div>
      </details>
      <details
        class="group rounded-xl border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50/80 transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden"
      >
        <summary
          class="flex items-center cursor-pointer px-6 py-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-orange-700 group-open:bg-amber-100/80 group-open:text-orange-900 transition-all duration-300"
        >
          <span
            class="mr-4 flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500 to-amber-600 flex items-center justify-center shadow-md"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 text-white"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              ><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M8 12l2 2 4-4"></path></svg
            >
          </span>
          Premium Materials & Craftsmanship
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6 pt-2 text-lg text-orange-800">
          We use only the finest materials and trusted artisans, ensuring your
          interiors are built to last and impress.
        </div>
      </details>
      <details
        class="group rounded-xl border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50/80 transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden"
      >
        <summary
          class="flex items-center cursor-pointer px-6 py-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-orange-700 group-open:bg-amber-100/80 group-open:text-orange-900 transition-all duration-300"
        >
          <span
            class="mr-4 flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-500 to-orange-600 flex items-center justify-center shadow-md"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 text-white"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              ><path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M12 8v4l3 3"></path></svg
            >
          </span>
          Transparent Process & Timely Delivery
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6 pt-2 text-lg text-orange-800">
          From concept to completion, we keep you informed and involved,
          delivering on time and within budget—always.
        </div>
      </details>
      <details
        class="group rounded-xl border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50/80 transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden"
      >
        <summary
          class="flex items-center cursor-pointer px-6 py-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-orange-700 group-open:bg-amber-100/80 group-open:text-orange-900 transition-all duration-300"
        >
          <span
            class="mr-4 flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-600 to-amber-500 flex items-center justify-center shadow-md"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 text-white"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              ><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 20h9"
              ></path><path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M12 4v16m8-8H4"></path></svg
            >
          </span>
          End-to-End Support & Aftercare
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6 pt-2 text-lg text-orange-800">
          Our relationship doesn’t end at handover. We’re here for you with
          ongoing support, advice, and maintenance tips.
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
